{"tid":866542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=street fight】工作問題爭執　粥店男工涉打傷女同事被捕","createTime":"2018-10-18T03:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T06:35:59.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cd1d52d3af6bed5f87fb8650fcce2f1d0b60a077","tid":866542,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T03:06:58.000Z","msg":"新蒲崗衍慶街一間粥店，今早(18日)9時13分，2名男女職員因工作問題爭執，其中男工涉以碗碟作武器，打傷該名女同事。警方接報趕至，當場拘捕涉案男工，女職員則報稱受傷送院。警方事後翻看店內的閉路電視，並取走錄影片段及一隻碗調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181018/bkn-20181018093158922-1018_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181018%2Fbkn-20181018093158922-1018_00822_001.html&d=u4stnqq8vOcMSVos4gNuvY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=891c0772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181018/bkn-20181018093158922-1018_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"551e401c4eec55df137aa5c2c3429976a7355385","tid":866542,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T03:07:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181018/photo/bkn-20181018093158922-1018_00822_001_01p.jpg?20181018110315\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181018%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181018093158922-1018_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20181018110315&h=42ad9e64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3e25a62eeba6321eb972071634177b308922ecf","tid":866542,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T03:08:09.000Z","msg":"並取走錄影片段及一隻碗調查<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一隻碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb38d8968db1c56798caf2404a2a073cd3cfe1d","tid":866542,"uid":205872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T03:12:14.000Z","msg":"取